740
00:51:19,129 --> 00:51:22,714
<i>The truth is, Norton wanted to size Andy up.</i>

741
00:51:36,354 --> 00:51:39,481
My wife made that in church group.

742
00:51:41,818 --> 00:51:43,152
Very nice, sir.

743
00:51:44,320 --> 00:51:46,196
Do you enjoy working in the laundry?

744
00:51:47,824 --> 00:51:49,533
No, sir, not especially.

745
00:51:49,617 --> 00:51:52,411
