753
00:52:14,767 --> 00:52:16,852
Ain't that a kick in the head?

754
00:52:16,936 --> 00:52:19,438
Well, I'll give you the dime tour.

755
00:52:19,522 --> 00:52:21,607
Come on.

756
00:52:21,691 --> 00:52:23,859
Well, here she is.

757
00:52:23,943 --> 00:52:26,486
Shawshank Prison library.

758
00:52:26,571 --> 00:52:29,448
National Geographics.

759
00:52:29,532 --> 00:52:32,367
Reader's Digest condensed books.

760
00:52:32,452 --> 00:52:34,745
Louis L'Amour.

761
00:52:34,746 --> 00:52:36,872
Look Magazine.

762
00:52:36,956 --> 00:52:39,458
Erle Stanley Gardners.

763
00:52:39,542 --> 00:52:43,086
