A letter a week. They can't ignore me forever.

820
00:55:51,359 --> 00:55:52,901
Sure can.

821
00:55:52,985 --> 00:55:55,862
But you write your letters, if it makes you happy.

822
00:55:55,947 --> 00:55:58,240
I'll even mail them for you. How's that?

823
00:56:00,159 --> 00:56:03,203
<i><font color="#808080">RED :</font> So, Andy started writing a letter a week,</i>

824
00:56:03,287 --> 00:56:05,372
<i>just like he said.</i>

825
00:56:09,419 --> 00:56:13,547
<i>And, just like Norton said, Andy got no answers.</i>

826
00:56:21,389 --> 00:56:26,893
<i>The following April, Andy did tax returns
