837
00:56:58,176 --> 00:57:01,219
<i>In fact, it got so busy at tax time...</i>

838
00:57:01,304 --> 00:57:03,346
<i>he was allowed a staff.</i>

839
00:57:03,431 --> 00:57:05,891
Hey, Red, can you hand me a stack of 1040s?

840
00:57:05,975 --> 00:57:08,643
<i>It got me out of the wood shop
a month out of the year,</i>

841
00:57:08,728 --> 00:57:11,396
<i>and that was fine by me.</i>

842
00:57:11,481 --> 00:57:14,858
<i>And still...he kept sending those letters.</i>

843
00:57:20,156 --> 00:57:21,990
Red, Andy.

844
00:57:22,074 --> 00:57:23,283
It's Brooks.

845
00:57:23,367 --> 00:57:25,827
<font color="#ff00ff">(Men shouting)</font>
- Watch the door.

846
00:57:25,912 --> 00:57:27,496
Please, Brooks.

847
00:57:27,580 --> 00:57:29,581
- Just calm the fuck down.
- Stay back!

848
00:57:29,665 --> 00:57:31,708
- Stay back!
