849
00:57:31,792 --> 00:57:34,878
You tell me. One second he's fine.
Then out comes the knife.

850
00:57:34,962 --> 00:57:37,422
Brooks, we can talk about this. Right?

851
00:57:37,507 --> 00:57:39,633
Nothing to talk about, goddamn it!

852
00:57:39,717 --> 00:57:41,426
I'm gonna cut his fucking throat.

853
00:57:41,511 --> 00:57:43,386
Heywood? Wait, what's he done to you?

854
00:57:43,471 --> 00:57:45,597
It's what they done!

855
00:57:45,681 --> 00:57:47,098
I...I got no choice...

856
00:57:47,183 --> 00:57:49,851
You're not gonna hurt him.
Even Heywood knows that.

857
00:57:49,936 --> 00:57:52,562
- Right, Heywood?
- I...I know that, sure.

858
00:57:52,647 --> 00:57:56,066
You won't hurt him, because he's a friend,
and you're a reasonable man.

859
00:57:56,150 --> 00:57:57,442
That's right. Right, guys?

860
00:57:57,527 --> 00:58:00,904
- Yes.
- So, put the knife down. Brooks, look at me.

861
00:58:00,988 --> 00:58:02,822
Put the knife down.

862
00:58:03,908 --> 00:58:05,075
Brooks...

863
00:58:05,159 --> 00:58:07,410
Look at his neck, for God's sake.

864
00:58:07,495 --> 00:58:09,829
Brooks, look at his neck. It's bleeding.

865
00:58:09,914 --> 00:58:11,081
<font color="#ff00ff">(Heywood gasps)</font>

866
00:58:11,165 --> 00:58:12,749
It's the only...

