882
00:59:01,173 --> 00:59:02,549
Would you knock it off?

883
00:59:02,633 --> 00:59:04,968
Brooks ain't no bug.

884
00:59:05,052 --> 00:59:06,928
He's just...

885
00:59:08,806 --> 00:59:10,640
He's just institutionalized.

886
00:59:11,976 --> 00:59:13,643
Institutionalized, my ass.

887
00:59:13,728 --> 00:59:18,023
