892
00:59:28,200 --> 00:59:30,827
Just a used-up con with arthritis in both hands.

893
00:59:30,911 --> 00:59:34,122
Probably couldn't get a library card if he tried.

894
00:59:34,206 --> 00:59:36,291
You know what I'm trying to say?

895
00:59:36,375 --> 00:59:39,127
Red, I do believe you're talking out of your ass.

896
00:59:40,379 --> 00:59:43,298
You believe whatever you want, Floyd.

897
00:59:43,299 --> 00:59:45,842
But I'm telling you, these walls are funny.

898
00:59:47,261 --> 00:59:49,346
First you hate 'em...

899
00:59:50,890 --> 00:59:52,974
..then you get used to 'em.

900
00:59:54,602 --> 00:59:57,228
Enough time passes...

901
00:59:57,313 --> 01:00:00,273
you get so you depend on 'em.

